hotspot.title: Hand Sanitizer
hotspot.description: Sanitize your hands, before entering the site and wear Visitor's Helmet. Keep safe distance (2m)

hotspot.title: Welcome to the Project Site
hotspot.description: 1. You are the Visiting Officer of this site. 2. Click blobbing hotspots to teleport around site vist tour. 3. Reach the site office to raise a Non-Confirmity and to start the Observation Sheet. 4. At the end of this tour you will receive your observation scores.

hotspot.title: Site Office
hotspot.description: Reach Site Office to raise Non-Confirmity

hotspot.title: Tour Guide
hotspot.description: 1. At the right side of the screen you will find the observation form to be filled while observing the site. 2. The site logistics is planned in zones, each zone has its observation tasks which needs to filled in the form. 3. If you have filled the form section of the respective zone, Map Button is provided at the top left side to open the site logistics plan. 4. At the end of this tour you will receive your observation scores.

hotspot.title: Site Office
hotspot.description: 1. Raise Non-Confirmity (NC) for Site Safety Barication 2. Preparation of Site Logistics Plan
